paragraphs.body: Bennett has voiced various characters in movies, TV shows, and video games and is considered "among the top names in the voice-over field". He voiced the Joker and other characters on Batman: The Brave and the Bold, Dorkus on Planet Sheen, Red Tornado on Young Justice, Keswick, Larry, and Ollie on T.U.F.F. Puppy, High-Five Ghost for the first season of Regular Show, Smee on Jake and the Never Land Pirates, and Kowalski in the ${link_0} series The Penguins of Madagascar.
